 <h1><i class="fa-regular fa-circle-question"></i> &nbsp; Help & Support Documentation</h1>
  <h2>Introduction</h2>
  <p>Struggling with something? We got you!</p>
  <p>This guide will help you navigate through the various features we offer.</p>

  <h2>Getting Started</h2>
  <ol>
    <li>
      <strong>Sign up</strong>
      <p>- To register please open the app and click on ‘Register Here’</p>
      <p>- Fill in your details</p>
      <p>- Make sure to read our Terms and Conditions</p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Login</strong>
      <p>- Once registered you will be redirected to the Login page</p>
      <p>- Enter you username/email and password</p>
    </li>
  </ol>

  <h2>Posts</h2>
  <ol>
    <li>
      <strong>Creating a post</strong>
      <p>- On the right column click on ‘Post Something’</p>
      <p>- Enter your message in the text box</p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Updating a post</strong>
      <p>- In the top right corner of the post click on the 3 dot button and select ‘Update post’</p>
      <p>- Edit the text in the text-box and post</p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Deleting a post</strong>
      <p>- In the top right corner of the post click on the 3 dot button and select ‘Delete post’</p>
      <p>- Click ‘Delete’ again in the confirmation pop up</p>
    </li>
  </ol>

  <h2>Updating your Profile</h2>
  <ol>
  	<li>
	  <p>On the top left corner click on the 3 lines dropdown button and select ‘Update Profile’</p>
	</li> 
	<li>
	  <p>Change the details you need to and click ‘Update Account’</p>
    </li>
 </ol>
  
  <h2>Deleting Account</h2>
  <ol>
    <li>
  	  <p>On the top left corner click on the 3 lines dropdown button and select ‘Delete Account’</p>
    </li>
    <li>
  	  <p>Click ‘Delete’ again in the confirmation pop up</p>
    </li>
  </ol>

